{
  "stem": "12494.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were sort of considered, on the one hand, as being the cream-- I'm talking about, that's the way were considered by the Jewish community, the people who-- the young people who made it in these difficult circumstances.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were all also the kids of rather influential and rich people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So in the Jewish Council, we have-- we were given all kinds of key spots.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My initial assignment was to essentially help getting apartments for the Germans, apartments or houses, for the Germans, per their request.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The German request would get in around 6 o'clock in the morning to the Jewish Council, and they would say, we need 18 apartments of roughly two rooms, with one bathroom, and we need six flats, two bathrooms, and six bedrooms, or whatever, and we need two villas.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then they would send us out, and-- that is the housing department, the lodging department of the council would send us out, always in groups of two.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they would give us a bunch of addresses, because the council had the list of all Jewish homes in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Or they thought they had the list of all Jewish homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These lists are never completely accurate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then we would go around and we would, by noon, have to come back and see-- we have notified the inhabitants of such and such apartment, or flat, or house, that they have to move out.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this is what we have accomplished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a fairly dirty job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish Council had places for them to go, other Jewish homes, and apartments, and flats.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a very difficult job.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
